game.name: Crossdress Wedding
game.description:
Your favorite Disney princesses look very happy today since they are going to tie a knot with their beloved princes.  All things will remain the same except their wedding dresses. This time they are not going to put on the gowns, but have decided to wear some more fancy outfits. We are pretty sure that you would have great fun while playing this brand new girls game. So why do you need to wait anymore? Join Crossdress Wedding and help them to pick up their dresses and see who looks best in the end!

Elsa, Jasmine and Mulan are preparing for the evening of their most awaited special day. They have faith on your fashion designer skills, so feel free to mix and match as many wedding dress options as you can to make them look fabulous on their special day. Remember this is a royal wedding so make sure to help them choose the best wedding dresses. It is up to you to help them attain an impressive wedding looks so that their statement looks can entertain their guests to the optimum possible level. 

You would get a chance to meet with the popular couples in this crodressing themed dress up game. Select the beautiful wedding outfits and suitable accessories for their grooms Aladdin, Jack Frost and Li Shang. There are multiple elegant traditional customs to choose from in their wardrobe. Make sure to complete their wedding looks with all the items available on the screen. Our website features a wide array of wedding games for girls and boys that you can enjoy for free online without download.
